There was a kid.
The kid didn't have a dog.
One day there was a dog.
The dog was standing at his door.
The dog didn't have a home.
He gave the dog food and water.
As time passed the boy started to love the dog.
And the dog started to love the boy.
The dog was happy.
The boy was happy too.
But once the dog bite the kid.
It was an accident.
The dog ran away.
The kid was sad.
The kid went after the dog.
It was raining.
The kid didn't give up.
He finnaly found the dog and took him home.
The kid was happy again.
They have become best friends.
The dog never ran away after that.
